    {
      "id": "8e5c8f17-cfd4-4b86-bb0c-bc13fc13dbc4",
      "name": "Sticky Note 3896af26",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [784, 256],
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## ⚙️ Setup Required\n\n**1. Base44 API Key credential:**\nNew → HTTP Header Auth\nHeader Name: `Authorization`\nHeader Value: `Bearer YOUR_AVUKA_APP_TOKEN`\n\n📌 To get token: log into avuka.base44.app → DevTools → Application → LocalStorage → copy `token`\n\n**2. Base44 Webhook:**\nFilledForm → action on status=completed → POST webhook URL with fields: `id`, `inspection_id`, `template_id`\n\nWebhook URL:\n`https://avuka.app.n8n.cloud/webhook/avuka-form-completed`\n\n**3. Supabase bucket:**\nBucket `fire-forms` must exist and be Public\n\n**Base44 Entity API:**\n`https://avuka.base44.app/api/apps/{appId}/entities/{EntityName}`\n\n**Base44 Function API:**\n`https://avuka.base44.app/functions/{functionName}`",
        "color": 2
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "8b8a97d8-5f6e-4bab-aaed-3682cb0523f6",
